StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetMOSE.ec.veDates]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@MOSCode varchar(4) AS
SELECT MOS.MOS_CODE, MOS.SHORT_DESCRIPTION, MC.MOS_CRITERIA_ED_DATE, MC.GENDER, CASE WHEN MC.STATUS IS NOT NULL THEN MC.STATUS ELSE 'A' END AS STATUS FROM [dbo].[MOS] WITH (NOLOCK) INNER JOIN [dbo].[MOS_CRITERIA] MC ON MOS.MOS_CODE = MC.MOS WHERE MOS.MOS_CODE = @MOSCode ORDER BY MC.MOS_CRITERIA_ED_DATE DESC
